                  <h3 class="blog-title">
                    <a href="/blog-details">
                      Scaling a SaaS API to 1M Requests
                    </a>
                  </h3>
                  <p class="p-md">
                    This case study breaks down the technical decisions behind
                    a high-throughput API redesign, including caching strategy,
                    async processing, and observability.
                  </p>
                  <p class="p-md">
                    The outcome was a 10x traffic increase with stable latency,
                    fewer incidents, and a simpler on-call experience.
                  </p>
                  <blockquote>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-right"></i>
                    �Measure the bottleneck, design the fix, and automate the
                    guardrails.�

                    <cite> Jordan Lee </cite>
                  </blockquote>
                  <h3 class="blog-title-second">Architecture decisions</h3>
                  <p>
                    We moved hot paths to edge caching, isolated background
                    jobs, and added rate limits with adaptive backoff for peak
                    traffic windows.
                  </p>
